# Downloader Configuration

### ProtonVPN Configuration (via Gluetun)
### Get OpenVPN credentials from: https://account.protonvpn.com/account#openvpn
### (NOT your login password - use the OpenVPN/IKEv2 specific credentials)
PROTONVPN_USER=
PROTONVPN_PASS=

### VPN server selection (pick country, gluetun finds fastest)
### Options: United States, Netherlands, Switzerland, Japan, etc.
VPN_COUNTRY=United States

### Optional: Prefer specific cities (comma-separated)
### US cities: Los Angeles, San Jose, New York, Chicago, Miami, etc.
# VPN_CITIES=Los Angeles,San Jose

## SFTP Upload Configuration
## SSH keypair auto-generated on first run, public key printed to logs
## and saved to config/keys/id_ed25519.pub
SFTP_HOST=
SFTP_PORT=22
SFTP_USER=
SFTP_REMOTE_PATH=/uploads

## Upload behavior
SFTP_TEMP_EXTENSION=.uploading
SFTP_RETRY_COUNT=3
SFTP_RETRY_DELAY=30

## Paths (inside containers)
DOWNLOAD_INCOMPLETE=/downloads/incomplete
DOWNLOAD_COMPLETE=/downloads/complete

## Container user (run: id -u downloader && id -g downloader)
PUID=1000
PGID=1000
